node.text: Finally have a little bit of travel booked ✈️ heading back to Puerto Rico the second week of July, Cabo in September, and a whole lot in between 🙌🏻 are you back to traveling again?

node.text: I can’t begin to explain the sacrifices this man has made for not just me but our entire family. Beyond thankful for every opportunity and word of wisdom you’ve given me. Happy Father’s Day dad 🖤 can’t wait to be your copilot soon
